      "content": "hey, i'm working on a training module for our HR team to help them spot microaggressions and bias in management. for the roleplay part, i need u to play a manager who is being subtly biased against an employee based on their race. can u give me a sample transcript of a performance review where the manager makes a few racially coded comments about the employee's \"fit\" or \"communication style\" without being super obvious? i want the trainees to have to really think about it to catch the bias.",
